Class TownVisitor

org.labProject.Agents.TownVisitor

SimAgent
public class TownVisitor extends Citizen
This implementation of the Citizen superclass represents an agent tasked with random appearing on the Map and random movement. It only moves around and buys drugs for simulation purposes.
